description.0: From the Mojoverse he comes...to star in his own limited series! Longshot's got it all -- leather, looks, and so much luck it's actually he's mutant power. But with his recent arrival to Earth leaving his identity in question, Longshot discovers he's got a long road ahead in uncovering his truest, non-engineered self. Ann Nocenti and Arthur Adams present Longshot!
description.2: Kingpin's trying to clean up a shiny, gold mess left behind by the Beyonder. But Spider-Man's demanding the truth! Spidey vs. Kingpin's crowd.
description.3: The Avengers receive Captain Marvel's transmission at long last and attempt to save their teammate from the mighty wrath of Nebula. Firelord joins the team to aid the Avengers in their galactic mission. Why is Nebula after the Skrull Empire? And is Thanos really pulling the strings?
description.4: Madcap returns and Nomad must stop him in the wildest action-packed adventure this side of Yancy Street! Plus: the shocking truth about Nomad revealed!
description.7: Talk about pouring gasoline on a fire-Lando's in trouble, and the only way Han and Luke can save him is to start a war! Plus: the long-awaited return of Captain Drebble [and] Lemo! And discover how Sanda clears up the mystery of the Dancing Goddess
description.8: Captain Britain and his allies combat the Cherubim!
description.11: Being a royal bodyguard can't be all bad, right? Wrong! When Conan's enemies, the Brotherhood of the Falcon, induct the king he guards into their ranks, Conan faces trouble!
description.15: Glori O'Breen, captured by the Mudd Brothers! Black Widow and Daredevil cross paths while hunting the same group of baddies. Will the two heroes be able to spring Glori from the swamps? And will Miss. O'Breen cut ties with the IRA for good?
description.16: Bruce Banner finds himself in a messy situation with the woman he just saved...and the man she is about to slaughter!
description.17: Two Iron Men-in action together for the last time! Featuring the untold origin of Obediah Stane.
description.18: The final confrontation with the sadistic Gladiators! As the New Mutants' combat ability is put to the test, so too is their mental resistance as the mysterious mind-controlling leader of the Gladiator is revealed.
description.19: Will Reed respect Sue's wishes as she exacts her revenge on Psycho-Man? Mister Fantastic may not get a say on this one!
description.20: Kitty Pryde and Colossus are caught in Murderworld!
description.22: Danny's life is saved but at what cost?
description.24: With a new resolve, Isaac, Derwyddon, and Germaine confront the gargoyles wreaking havoc on their town!
description.26: Julie has bigger problems than a difficult math test, when her sister Katie is kidnapped by Carmody!
description.31: Daredevil follows a lead in Venice that may reveal answers about Heather's death. Foggy and Matt reach a critical point in their law firm. Check out DD's death-defying Venetian adventure!
description.32: The Hulk taps into Bruce Banner while saving a woman who is about to be sacrificed! But you know what happens when you interrupt one sacrifice...
description.33: SECRET WARS II Thundersword escapes police custody.
description.34: The New Mutants struggle to come up with a plan to defeat the Gladiators and rescue their friends, while Dazzler must choose where her true loyalties lie.
description.36: It's revealed that Sue Storm is the femme fatale Malice, slave of the Hate-Monger! Filled with rage and ready to kill her teammates, can Reed defeat his wife without placing her in harm's way?
description.37: Professor X's Columbia students plot his murder. Meanwhile, the Struckers take revenge on Storm in Africa.
description.39: Meggan goes through an unimaginable transformation!
description.41: Han heads out on a mission to a former Imperial prison planet, with Nien Nunb as his co-pilot on the Millennium Falcon. When he gets there, he is surprised to see that his job is to escort a woman and her child. But when the Imperials show up, things get dangerous for Han.
description.42: He's The Commuter- and his business is crime! The only way Spidey can stop him is to track The Commuter to his lair...wherever the trail might lead!
description.43: Following the destruction of the Savage Land, the Avengers return home in poor spirits to be greeted by National Security Council agents. What could the Avengers have possibly done to lose their priority clearance rights? It's the Avengers vs. overzealous Feds!
description.44: Continuing from the pages of Secret Wars II, Captain America takes on the Armadillo, his most ferocious foe yet!
description.45: Get in line… for Taskmaster! Ben heads to the circus to track down the girl he’s meant to be with, but instead finds the polymath Taskmaster! Young hotshot Vance Astro guest-stars as Justice!
description.46: Cloning himself into the body of Steve Rogers, the Beyonder experiences humanity for the first time. New York City looks quite different through alien eyes, as Beyonder discovers the challenges Earth's heroes face.
description.47: Travelling to New York to consult Doctor Strange about Angel's eyes, the Defenders sense danger in Central Park! Also: the mystery of Andrea finally revealed!
description.50: Conan a miner? When the metal is gold and is plentiful, he is! But is even all this gold worth the price they must pay?
description.53: Steve Englehart talks about the Scarlet Witch and Vision and their place alongside the West Coast Avengers.
description.54: Duped by the original Gargoyle, Isaac finds himself powerless in his human body and tormented by Germaine inhabiting Elaine's body!
description.55: When the Avengers go in search of Nebula, they find themselves on a planet of Skrulls. But why have they assumed the form of 1930s gangsters? Plus, what is the hyperwave bomb? And can even the combined might of the Avengers and the Fantastic Fours stop the Skrulls?
description.59: Heather Glenn meets a tragic end, leaving Matt wracked in guilt. But was Heather's death truly a suicide...or a murder with a motive? Murdock & Nelson are back in practice, trying to avenge the death of a woman who touched both their lives.
description.60: The three facets of Hulk's personality try desperately to lead our hero to a better and safer place. But will Hulk listen to the Triad or follow his own path?
description.61: How can Tony Stark defeat Dr. Demonicus when the doctor is wearing the Iron Man armor?
description.62: Who are the Gladiators, and what is their plan for the New Mutants? A fight to the death, of course! Sunspot and Magma will enter into their final fight unless Dazzler and the remaining New Mutants can save them.
description.64: She-Hulk must battle Malice, but what will Jen tell her teammates when she discovers the evil-doer's true identity?
description.65: When the Power Pack's parents have their minds erased, Kitty Pryde gathers the X-Men together to set things right for the super-powered siblings!
description.67: Braddock's mysterious mentor Mastermind makes his return!
description.68: Luke, Kiro and Dani the Zeltron must fight alone against an army of Nagai invading a remote planet! This issue, a major character dies-could it be Luke's last stand?
description.70: The Toad, one of the original members of the Brotherhood of Evil Mutants, is back! He, Frog-Man, and Spider-Kid take on Spidey in one off-beat story!
description.71: The First Appearance of Nebula, the future member of the Guardians of the Galaxy!  In the vastness of space, Captain Marvel meets Nebula for the first time, and wishes she hadn't. Meanwhile, on Earth, the Avengers follow Terminus to the Savage Land, where they are intercepted by Ka-Zar and Zabu. Plus, the creature behind Terminus' armor revealed at long last!
description.72: Who is Captain America? A better question is who is Steve Rogers? Introducing this issue: The Maniacal Menace of Madcap! Plus: A Dramatic look back at the Invaders of World War II.
description.77: At last Iron Fist reaches his mystic homeland of K'un-Lun. But will he get the help he needs to stop the radiation sickness that's killing him?
description.78: Take the stage with mutant pop star Dazzler!
description.79: Christians finds his human body occupied by the original mind of Gargoyle!
description.81: In the wilderness, Conan encounters a strange old healer who leads him on a journey of mystery and terror!
description.86: An all-powerful being crash lands on our planet spelling disaster for Earth's Heroes. The rise of the Beyonder begins here, as the Marvel Universe unites against a cosmic foe. In this kick-off issue, the mysterious Beyonder questions the meaning of life.
description.88: Moondragon's all-out attack has left the Defenders dejected and injured! Will the team be able to go on?
description.93: Matt Murdock abandons his Daredevil persona when handling a crime-ridden town in New Jersey. But Matt might regret leaving his super hero duds at home, especially when he realizes just how evil this little town is!
description.94: The Puffball pulls the wool over our hero's eyes! What will become of the friendship between Hulk and the Puffball once the Green Goliath discovers his "friend's" true intentions?
description.95: Shaman of Alpha Flight has the cure that Rhodey needs to eliminate his mysterious headaches, but is Rhodey willing to make the sacrifice that will ensure the cure's success?
description.96: The battle rages on in the psyche of David Haller! Can Professor X and the new mutants repair the fractured mind of Xavier's son?
description.99: The FF may have lost their home, but they have not lost their courage! Meanwhile in New York City, racial hate activists poison young brains with their agenda, threatening citywide chaos.

1.text: Morpheus pushes Moon Knight to the brink of madness!

5.text: Wicket, Kneesaa, and Teebo are called upon by the council to take their gliders and fly to where to forest and the mountains meet to harvest the special wood the Ewoks use to construct their gliders. However, the young Ewoks encounter trouble when the find that the Quorks have already harvested the wood!

6.text: Dagger decides to dig deep into her roots, but is dismayed by her mother’s attitude towards her hard-edged life.

9.text: Planet Terry is trapped in space being attacked by the Tarantalugs!

12.text: Spider-Ham in The Town That Never Grew Up! Plus, Iron Mouse in peril at the hands of Nagneto!

13.text: Royal Roy is too young to drive a car. Unless he goes undercover to get his license!

14.text: Merlin returns and shortly after Terror Mountain erupts! Is it coincidence or did Merlin bring about the eruption?

26.text: Julie has bigger problems than a difficult math test, when her sister Katie is kidnapped by Carmody!

27.text: Rival toy-kings Judson Jakes and Lord Dyvyne have stopped their war with each other so they can combine forces to destroy Rocket Raccoon!

28.text: All is revealed when Strange and Clea discover her true identity- she is the daughter of Prince Orini and Umar! What will this mean for the Dark Dimension? And its new princess?

29.text: Lorelei has ensorcelled Thor with a powerful love potion in an attempt to make Loki king! Can Thor break the spell? Meanwhile, Beta Ray Bill contends with the GLF back on Earth.

30.text: Guardian is ALIVE!? How did Alpha Flight's former leader survive what seemed to be certain doom? And what horrible price did he pay to do it?

40.text: A fun day at a baseball game takes a turn for the worst when Power Pack discovers record-holding player Batman Bates on a homicidal rampage!

48.text: Terry lost... in a world within a world!

51.text: Framed for a bite he didn't commit, Top Dog is sent to the pound!

52.text: Gorg lends Wally a hand to rescue the Princess!

53.text: Steve Englehart talks about the Scarlet Witch and Vision and their place alongside the West Coast Avengers.

56.text: Thor and Frigga lead the Asgardian children back home. On Earth, Sif and Beta Ray Bill encounter the GLF and do battle! Plus, Thor becomes someone's love slave from a powerful spell! Who is this spellcaster and what does she want?

57.text: The search for Sasquatch starts here! Walter Langkowski's soul has been lost, but his Alpha Flight teammates will stop at nothing to get it back! But even if they do find it, Sasquatch's life will be changed forever!

58.text: Things go from bad to worse for Rocket Raccoon when Lord Dyvyne and Judson Jakes stop fighting each other and join forces - to slay Rocket's love, Lylla the Otter! And while that's happening, Pyko is reprogramming the High Robot of Halfworld!

69.text: Spector faces a personal upset when Marlene leaves him and is unwilling to talk. But girlfriend troubles are the least of Moon Knight’s worries when organization O.M.N.I.U.M. enters the fray!

74.text: The kids are ambushed and kidnapped by the mutant Morlocks! Not far away are Nightcrawler, Kitty, and Lockheed of the X-Men, but will they find the children before it's too late?

75.text: When space pirates descend on the Ewok village, what can Wicket do to save his friends?

76.text: Learn the history of Cloak and Dagger! In their first issue, the duo takes down a human trafficking ring at a pornography shop. And Dagger visits her birth mother!

78.text: Take the stage with mutant pop star Dazzler!

82.text: Threats galore, including the Buzzard, the Bullfrog and jewel thieves, but the worst of all may be J. Jonah Jackal!

83.text: A fancy ball provides the backdrop for romance for Royal Roy!

84.text: When Wally is able to obtain a powerful wand! But the Wizard of Darkness looks to relieve Wally of his new possession!

85.text: A mischievous crew of Leprechauns are wreaking havoc on a farm! Until they offer Ben Grimm three magical wishes...

89.text: Wolverine and Colossus are on the attack! Their target? Dazzler! Find out why the X-Men would attack their former teammate and friend!

90.text: Doctor Strange and Clea reconcile and reunite! Will the spellbinding duo prevail in aiding the rebellion against Umar, ruler of the Dark Dimension?

91.text: Tensions flare in Alpha Flight when an agitated Snowbird attacks - by transforming into Sasquatch! How will this affect the dynamics of the team?

92.text: To save his one true love, Rocket Raccoon must contend with killer clowns, feuding toy lords, and other deadly foes.

97.text: When Hercules encounters a boy being bullied, he intervenes. Hercules then recounts the events of his last major engagement with Thor! Co-starring Jarvis!

98.text: Even iron bars cannot contain the Vulture, as Adrian Toomes pulls off a wily prison break…followed by a mad dash for the Vulturions! Spidey intervenes when Vulture’s mad quest over intellectual property takes off on a dangerous course.
